summary: This is an email chain from October 18, 2019, discussing an upcoming meeting scheduled for the following Wednesday at 10 AM in New York, described as an 'Epstein victims' meeting'. The correspondence is between Laura Birger and another individual, with the subject 'Re: The Week Ahead'.

persons.name: Laura Birger
persons.context: Appears as the sender/recipient in an email chain discussing the scheduling of an Epstein victims' meeting. Her email address indicates affiliation with the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).

events.title: Epstein victims' meeting in New York
events.description: A meeting concerning victims of Jeffrey Epstein is scheduled for 10 AM on a Wednesday, which based on the email date of October 18, 2019, would be October 23, 2019.

keyFacts: An 'Epstein victims' meeting' was scheduled for a Wednesday at 10 AM in New York in October 2019.
The email correspondence involves Laura Birger, whose address indicates she was with the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
The document is a brief scheduling email, highlighting ongoing official activity related to Epstein victims in late 2019, after Epstein's death in August of that year.
